Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.43,0:01:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第38届 苍荣高中文化祭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要开幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.98,0:01:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时都可以
